<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka Tanpa khawi a um na him?
 Ti'n ka hun hawl viel viel hi;
 Kei di'n thil lopi nei guotsak a,
 Ka kumsawt van nawpna ding.

[V2]
 Aw, Ka Tanpa lopi pen,
 Aw, ka Hukdampa mak pen;
 Kei di'n thing hansie dawlah Na hung thuok,
 Ka Lal leh tanpa na hi.

[V3]
 2. Na hehpihna thuk leh let zie,
 Kuoman a mu pha ngei puou;
 Van mi thiengthote cheng cheng in le,
 A thuk zie a mu pha puou.

[V4]
 3. Sietlei a Na hung lai guol khan,
 Tuhin ka hun mu thei puoi;
 Mahleh nei hehpihna thu nutsieh,
 Ka lunggil ah a cham zing.

[V5]
 4. Aw, ka thagau chieh zel in la,
 Na Tanpa Lal kawm a chun;
 A khut changlam akhun va chun la,
 Na kumsawt khawpi achun.</lyrics>
<title>WHERE ART THOU?</title>
</song>